xPL TTS
========

These modules are intended to provide a small TTS client for Perl
Installation

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

Test: 
   xpl-hub should already be running 
      xpl-hub -i eth0 

   

Dependencies
   * sudo apt-get install libyaml-perl

   * xpl-perl
     git clone  https://github.com/beanz/xpl-perl/
     cd xpl-perl 
     perl Makefile.PL
      make
      make test
      make install

   * mpg321
      sudo apt-get install mpg321 


